    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "A tiny yellow duckling bobs playfully through the splashing water puddle. Calling out merrily, it encourages others with: \"Quack! Quack! The duck says: 'Follow me!'\"",
      "source_page_number": 5,
